<div class="content-narrow legal-page">
    <section class="page-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Site information</p>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p class="subtitle">
            Effective July 17, 2026
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-card legal-content">
        <p>
            Sunset Guardian respects your privacy. This page explains what
            information may be collected when you visit this website and how
            that information is used.
        </p>

        <h2>Information collected automatically</h2>

        <p>
            Sunset Guardian uses analytics services to understand which pages
            are visited, how visitors find the site, and how well the site
            performs.
        </p>

        <h3>Cloudflare Web Analytics</h3>

        <p>
            Cloudflare Web Analytics provides information such as page views,
            visits, referral sources, browser types, approximate geographic
            regions, and website performance measurements.
        </p>

        <p>
            Cloudflare describes its Web Analytics service as privacy-focused
            and states that it collects these website measurements without
            using cookies.
        </p>

        <h3>Google Analytics</h3>

        <p>
            Sunset Guardian also uses Google Analytics. Google Analytics may
            collect information about pages viewed, links selected, browser
            and device characteristics, approximate location, referral
            sources, and interactions with the website.
        </p>

        <p>
            Google Analytics uses cookies and similar identifiers to measure
            website activity. Sunset Guardian does not intentionally send
            names, email addresses, phone numbers, account numbers, or other
            directly identifying information to Google Analytics.
        </p>

        <p>
            Learn more about how Google uses information from sites that use
            its services:
            <a
                href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
                How Google uses information
            </a>.
        </p>

        <h2>How information is used</h2>

        <p>
            Analytics information may be used to:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Understand which tools and articles visitors find useful</li>
            <li>Improve website navigation and content</li>
            <li>Identify technical problems</li>
            <li>Measure website speed and reliability</li>
            <li>Understand general traffic and referral patterns</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Information you provide</h2>

        <p>
            Sunset Guardian currently does not require visitor accounts,
            subscriptions, purchases, or calculator data submissions.
            Calculator entries are processed in your browser and are not
            intentionally sent to Sunset Guardian.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-party services</h2>

        <p>
            Sunset Guardian relies on third-party services including
            Cloudflare and Google. These providers process information under
            their own terms and privacy policies.
        </p>

        <h2>External links</h2>

        <p>
            Articles may link to websites operated by other organizations.
            Sunset Guardian is not responsible for the privacy practices,
            security, or content of outside websites.
        </p>

        <h2>Children’s privacy</h2>

        <p>
            Sunset Guardian is intended for a general audience and is not
            directed toward children under 13. The site does not knowingly
            collect personal information from children.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>

        <p>
            This policy may be updated when the site adds features, services,
            advertising, or different analytics tools. The effective date at
            the top of this page will be updated when material changes are
            made.
        </p>

        <h2>Questions</h2>

        <p>
            Contact information for privacy questions will be added before
            Sunset Guardian begins accepting messages or other personal
            information through the website.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>
